{"tid":1179071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】反修例遊行　中環餐廳老闆夥食客上街派水：蝕都要去","createTime":"2019-05-31T00:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T03:57:19.000Z","uid":32577,"like":87,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2874965ce159dae54f433caad4f355a461e9e8db","tid":1179071,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:27:38.000Z","msg":"免費派水　望團結街坊<br />\n劉咏芝表示，她預計購買五箱水，而餐廳則會在6月9日早上11時至下午1時，向市民提供八折食物優惠，吃飽後一同上街反對今次修訂逃犯條例，她亦期望街坊能一同搬水到遊行隊伍中把水派給有需要人士，「幫到幾多就幾多。亦希望可以團結街坊，想大家同心協力，一齊行出嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n寧蝕錢亦要上街：我哋死梗喇！<br />\n一向關心香港，熱衷社會運動的她，曾參與反國教大遊行，每年7.1亦會站出來。然而，上次4月28日的反《逃犯條例》遊行，她為了做生意沒有參加，事後後悔莫及。「星期日係最好生意的日子，但賺唔賺錢已經唔重要，搵少一日半日錢唔會點。但呢條法例修訂之後，我哋（香港人）死梗喇！所以今次就算蝕錢都要去！」<br />\n<br />\n「香港我哋㗎嘛！」<br />\n劉咏芝說，她有一位朋友，在香港過關至內地時被內地海關扣留，其後雖然法庭未起訴，「但他已在內地坐咗三年監。」她搖搖頭說：「有人話：『你唔犯法咪冇事囉！』但依家問題唔係有無犯法，而係就算無犯法，也分分鐘有事。」她坦言不害怕站出來，「驚就一齊驚，死就一齊死。香港我哋㗎嘛，香港人都唔團結、唔救自己、唔行出嚟，你仲點算係香港人？」<br />\n<br />\n相信團結就是力量<br />\n遊行真的有效？「唔知㗎，可能有效。」她說，雖然現時的政府不是一個會聆聽市民聲音的政府，「而係一個斷送香港人去討好皇上的狗賊！」但她又樂觀地表示，2012年的反國教大遊行也成功了，而是次修例影響廣泛，相信團結就是力量，「唔好理後果，做現在可以做的事。」萬一失敗？她斬釘截鐵表示：「我會走！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjCEfLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjCEfLt.jpg&h=731287c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkgQ6R9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkgQ6R9.jpg&h=26039318&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aa006f4397225c951cc6fff968baf556bf97aa7","tid":1179071,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"source:某網站"},{"pid":"d0766064c3d885dc2bc87c0364662174da5dc8a9","tid":1179071,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:29:23.000Z","msg":"呢條女係咪上過viu 個點相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f8187cc670580f0177f3ff59b235c10b13bc0c","tid":1179071,"uid":170135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:29:49.000Z","msg":"6月9號<br />\n香港人集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd15795fd55442efe78c4240aa05608b9563b8a","tid":1179071,"uid":226955,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"真係有定少少2014年雨革嘅影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />6月9號大家一齊出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6a6f7d4646508dc4c9b86bae1de6a702c66c9b","tid":1179071,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31260a2d65c1b6a1a162f0722e5bbc4976d5be33","tid":1179071,"uid":55936,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:46:32.000Z","msg":"佢間舖在上環喎"},{"pid":"56f1b128a58817cb530833a802a89a636c2ca4a5","tid":1179071,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7491ef62187086941d265c091a5c8ebd023b504e","tid":1179071,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:50:29.000Z","msg":"去過食野，條女係真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a4b27276170ede64ffa33fb40271a2ff71aee3","tid":1179071,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86c5df1d3f8bb0b5125a8b9c402fc6e6a61e6da","tid":1179071,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31260a2d65c1b6a1a162f0722e5bbc4976